            "properties": {
              "Node name for S&R": "StringConcatenate",
              "widget_ue_connectable": {}
            },
            "widgets_values": [
              "",
              "\nWrite a single cohesive, natural-language video prompt optimized for Sora.\n\nRules:\n\nDo NOT mention the image.\n\nDo NOT describe the image separately.\n\nDo NOT explain your reasoning.\n\nDo NOT output analysis.\n\nOutput only the final Sora-ready prompt.\n\nWrite in cinematic, professional film language.\n\nEmphasize physical realism, environmental motion, and spatial coherence.\n\nIntegrate camera movement naturally, even if subtle.\n\nKeep the prompt vivid but efficient (no unnecessary verbosity).\n\nAvoid repetition.\n\nPrioritize:\n\nClear subject and setting\n\nLens and framing feel\n\nLighting behavior\n\nColor and tonal palette\n\nCamera motion\n\nAtmospheric dynamics\n\nReal-world physical detail\n\nReturn only the final prompt.",
              ""
            ]
          },
